overview.en: BQT is the community proof of stake of BQI which is committed to blockchain and the big data quotation of cryptocurrency. BQI provides standard data output to blockchain industry in an open manner.It makes use of its own data flow and industry data related to create the application for blockchain industry. BQI promotes its community values and connect all users and members via BQT.
overview.zh: BQT是BQI生态的社区权益证明（Community Proof Of Stake），BQI.COM生态致力于区块链以及虚拟货币行情大数据，以开放的形式给区块链行业提供标准的数据输出，利用自身的流量以及相关行业数据，打造区块链行业数据应用，用来粘合整个行业相关生态。
